com.cerner.beadledom.jaxrs

Class GenericResponseBuilder<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cerner.beadledom.jaxrs.GenericResponseBuilder<T>

  • public abstract class GenericResponseBuilder<T>
extends Object
    A class for building GenericResponse instances.

    An initial instance of a builder can be obtained via the static methods of the GenericResponses class.

    Since:
    1.3
    Author:
    John Leacox
